summary: “You said you loved me,” Harry said, trying to keep his voice from cracking, “you told me that you wouldn’t do this, and now...
question: “You said you loved me,” Harry said, trying to keep his voice from cracking, “you told me that you wouldn’t do this, and now you’re with him?” Feeling the heaviness of her heart she looked down, “I’m sorry, I do love you, it just sort of happened.” “You falling in love with my best friend ‘just sort of happened’?” Harry asked, tears now threatening to fall.
